items.title: 8-Minute Empire
items.details:
When: Fri 25 Jul 2014 16:00 to 17:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: 2 to 5 players take turns selecting a card displayed. Cards have goods and actions on them, actions are used to take over the map and sets of goods are worth points at the end. Getting the right balance is key to victory.

items.title: Ricochet Robots
items.details:
When: Fri 25 Jul 2014 15:00 to 16:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Moving robots to the target chips, when a robot sets off it goes until it hits a wall or another robot.

items.title: SET
items.details:
When: Fri 25 Jul 2014 14:00 to 15:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Can you spot the three cards that have their features either all the same or all different?

items.title: Pucket - Competition
items.details:
When: Thu 24 Jul 2014 22:00 to 23:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Pucket Competition starts after the open stage, a knock out tournement to determine the EJC Pucket champion.

items.title: Pucket
items.details:
When: Thu 24 Jul 2014 16:00 to 17:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Pucket is a two-player game where both players are trying to flick through their pucks (at the same time) to the other side before the opposite player can empty their side.

items.title: Say bye to Villians
items.details:
When: Thu 24 Jul 2014 15:00 to 16:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: 3 to 8 players work together to share information to collectively defeat a villian, through discarding cards to learn hidden information, taking special training and taking special actions can you work together to win?

items.title: Mascarade
items.details:
When: Thu 24 Jul 2014 14:00 to 15:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: 2 to 13 players enter the mascarade and unmask your opponents! Assuming the role of up to 13 different characters with the ultimate goal of being the richest player by the end of the game.

items.title: One Night Werewolf
items.details:
When: Wed 23 Jul 2014 16:00 to 17:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: 3 to 10 players play the classic werewolf game over a one night period, no-one dies while everyone tries to work out who the werewolves are?! Kill a werewolf villagers win, kill a villager werewolves win!

items.title: Hanabi
items.details:
When: Wed 23 Jul 2014 15:00 to 16:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: 2 to 5 players work together to build the best firework display possible. No-one gets to see their cards and on your go give information if you can, play or discard a card. This game won the speile des jahre 2013.

items.title: Splendor
items.details:
When: Wed 23 Jul 2014 14:00 to 15:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Splendor is a 2 to 4 player game, where you try to collect gems to gain you prestrige points, by either collecting coins or buying cards.

items.title: Battle Sheep - Competition
items.details:
When: Tue 22 Jul 2014 22:00 to 23:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Battle Sheep competiton starting after the Irish Gala Show, can you be the best player of the EJC?

items.title: Battle Sheep
items.details:
When: Tue 22 Jul 2014 16:00 to 17:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Battle Sheep is for 2 to 4 players, guide your sheep and try and block your opponents from taking all the pastures. A lovely mixture of family fun and strategy at its best.

items.title: Dodekka
items.details:
When: Tue 22 Jul 2014 15:00 to 16:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Dodekka is a 2 to 6 player game where you are trying to collect the highest score of one type of element. Take a card or turn a card, just becareful if the total of cards on the table goes over 12 you have to take them all!

items.title: Swish
items.details:
When: Tue 22 Jul 2014 14:00 to 15:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Swish is a good way increasing your spatiacal IQ! Everyone tries to work put which cards go to gether to make a complete circles of all the colours on them.

items.title: Tichu - Competition
items.details:
When: Mon 21 Jul 2014 22:00 to 23:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: The Tichu competition will start tonight and carry on throughout the week. Playing in pairs you will have 4 hands per game keeping the points you win. The team that gains the most points wins.

items.title: Tichu - Intermediates
items.details:
When: Mon 21 Jul 2014 16:00 to 17:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Tichu for intermediates, following on from the beginners workshop and assuming you know how to play, we will go through all stages of a round explaining best practices on when to play. when not to play.

items.title: Tichu - Beginners
items.details:
When: Mon 21 Jul 2014 15:00 to 16:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Tichu for beginners is aim for people who have never played Tichu before. I will go through the games, describing cards and playable hands. Strategy and tatics will be discuss more in the intermediate workshop.

items.title: Dominion
items.details:
When: Mon 21 Jul 2014 14:00 to 15:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Dominion is a 2 to 4 Card game where you are trying to build your own personal decks to get a mixture of actions and money to enable you to buy better land. Brilliant game that started the genre of deck building games.

items.title: Elk Fest Competition
items.details:
When: Sun 20 Jul 2014 22:00 to 23:59  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Starting after the Open stage, take part in the Elk Fest knock out competition, can you become the EJC Elk Fest Champion?

items.title: Elk Fest
items.details:
When: Sun 20 Jul 2014 16:00 to 17:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Elk Fest, this two-player dexerity game requires you to try and get your Elk's to the opposite side of the swamp by flicking the stones in to the right place. Fun and simple.

items.title: Love Letter
items.details:
When: Sun 20 Jul 2014 15:00 to 16:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Love Letter is a 2 to 4 Person game where you are trying to get your love letter to the Princess. You start with one character and draw another, playing one of them. All characters have special actions and when you play them the affect takes place. Be the last one in a round or the character closest to the Princess to win.

items.title: Citadels
items.details:
When: Sun 20 Jul 2014 14:00 to 15:00  IST

Where: Lazy Juggler Area
Event Status: confirmed
Event Description: Citadels is a 2 to 7 person straetgy game, where each round you choose a from a selection of available characters and try to gain gold to get 8 buildings in your district.
